Author: baronofficiall2
Title: [ANN] iShooK - eBooks with Social Media all in One - Tokensale 8th Jan 2018
Body: Nowadays, books, newspapers and magazines on paper are gradually taking the place of digital content. Now people read their books with e-book readers, access to newspapers and magazines via the web. Platforms that share existing digital content are often far from appealing to inadequate and widespread mass. At the same time, content owners especially have to spend a lot of time and effort on different platforms to advertise their content, sell, and receive payments. IShook is currently a working platform and wants to update its infrastructure with block-chain technology. Ishookun is open to the access of tens of thousands of book archive users in the current platform. Thousands of people benefit from this archive every day. IShookun aims to create a comprehensive social network of digital content such as electronic books and magazines. Through this network, content creators and content creators will interact directly. Content owners will be able to publish, sell, and advertise all their content through this platform. On the other hand, readers who search for content will be able to obtain their content from individual content creators and share their views and notes about the content through the social platform. This way a feedback archive will be created and all users will be able to benefit from these feedbacks. The development and operational activities of the Ishook team platforms have also created a token (SHK) to ensure the flow of digital money in the platform.    Those who have the SHK token are on the platform; - they will be able to access discounted content and electronic data. -The money transfers in the platform can be carried out without intermediaries and at the same time only the SHK token owners will be able to access hidden content created by Content providers.
